imdb.plot outline: Puenteviejo, 1902. Pepa midwife comes to Puenteviejo to exercise her profession. Her faith leads her to cross paths with Francisca Montenegro, landowner, and stepmother of Carlos Castro, a ex lover of Pepa and father of her child, a boy who was ripped from Pepa at birth... Pepa believed her son had died, but then she realizes that Martin is actually her real son. From that moment Pepa fights to regain what is hers, and on the way find love in the arms of Tristan.
